    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car! It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who needs a dependable daily driver. I've taken great care of it, and it\u2019s ready to hit the road for many more miles. It\u2019s got that perfect balance of being well-loved but still looking and driving great. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 34500.0,
