      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies consistent performance and structural integrity. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection, ensuring it meets our rigorous standards for roadworthiness and mechanical reliability. A premier choice for the discerning driver seeking a balance of sophisticated engineering and proven value.",
      "price": 32500.0,
