    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's looking for a new home! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape, running smoothly and ready for many more adventures. I\u2019ve kept up with the maintenance, so you're getting a great car that's been truly cared for. If you're looking for something dependable and high-quality that's ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 31500.0,
