    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this E46 M3, a testament to naturally aspirated precision. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system that pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and delivered through a limited-slip differential. This example boasts essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the chassis and bottom end are track-ready. Finished with a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers, the steering remains communicative and the turn-in sharp. A mechanically robust driver\u2019s car that prioritizes performance and structural integrity.",
